 auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Billionaires (and trillionaires now I guess) all got that way from the exploitation inherent to capitalism btw…</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rfo9NHp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The green part is how they become billionaires. Yes we could tax them out of existence, we could also just stop them from taking what’s rightfully ours in the first place.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lJKqfn8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>If you’re wondering what that looks like:</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/y5sjZ0Y</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Mgxr44]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Let's send food to Imgurians in need</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/k5EuLvi</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0rTIDri.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Happy Saturday everyone, we're all excited for TheFreePizzaDude post today!

If you'd like to help a struggling Imgurian get groceries or a meal today there are 2 easy ways -</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MLcRrnR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>You can find a request for food in the comments, reply to them and then send a DM to get an order set up

Or you can contribute to the Imgurian Meal Fund and we'll send the food for you!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nrFzKqQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Anonymous Angels have been a big help in feeding more people, we love you so much!

https://www.paypal.me/TheFreePizzaDude

https://ko-fi.com/thefreepizzadude</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uEFLjci.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And here's how you'd send it yourself!

Any questions as an Angel?

Just shoot us a message!

We'll be on this username until 6pm central</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dXiEssR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Kevin and his tongue are here to show you how it works for requests -</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FoHhAnm.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's much easier for us to help requests in the US but we'll do our best to pick up requests from any country.

Putting your country in your comment helps us match you to an Angel in your area</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OrUWTjk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Any questions as a requestor?

Just leave a comment!

